OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,FA man who waited 90 minutes to call
OL,8,F999 after attacking his partner until
OL,9,Fshe fell unconscious has been found
OL,10,Fguilty of her murder.
OL,12,FDale Vincent Cole, 39, of Grange
OL,13,FStreet, Burton-on-Trent, attacked his
OL,14,Fpartner of five years, Lisa Holland,
OL,15,Fat her home in Victoria Crescent in
OL,16,Fthe town on October 20, 2022.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
