OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,FCole rang 999 at 6.23pm, 90 minutes
OL,8,Fafter Staffordshire Police said
OL,9,Fevidence showed she was unconscious,
OL,10,Fand claimed to emergency services she
OL,11,Fhad fallen down the stairs.
OL,13,FBy the time ambulance crews arrived
OL,14,Fshe had already died. Cole was
OL,15,Farrested a short time later on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of her murder.
OL,18,FCole was found guilty of murder at
OL,19,FStafford Crown Court today, Friday,
OL,20,FMarch 20. He had been charged with the
OL,21,Foffence last July.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,FHe had earlier pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, controlling or coercive
OL,9,Fbehaviour in an intimate or family
OL,10,Frelationship, and to one count of
OL,11,Finflicting grievous bodily harm.
OL,13,FLisa's family paid tribute to her
OL,14,Ffollowing the trial.
OL,16,FThey said: "Her death has left an
OL,17,Funmeasurable void in the lives of us
OL,18,Fwho love her so dearly.
OL,26,@xD@LOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
