OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,F"Lisa's illuminating smile and
OL,8,Finfectious laughter would light up any
OL,9,Froom.
OL,11,F"She was an incredibly beautiful lady
OL,12,Fboth inside and out, who loved and
OL,13,Fcared so very deeply for her family
OL,14,Fand those around her.
OL,16,FDet Chief Insp Ian Fitzgerald, of
OL,17,FStaffordshire Police's major
OL,18,Finvestigations department, said: "Lisa
OL,19,FHolland should be alive today.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUzD@bOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,F"She was a vulnerable woman who was
OL,8,Fsystematically controlled, isolated
OL,9,Fand brutalised by a man who saw her as
OL,10,Fsomeone he could dominate without
OL,11,Fconsequence.
OL,13,F"Cole was a violent bully who
OL,14,Fweaponised Lisa's vulnerabilities to
OL,15,Fmaintain power over her.
OL,17,F"He punished her with regular, severe
OL,18,Fbeatings and denied her the dignity,
OL,19,Fsafety and care every person deserves.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
