CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774033869
OL,3,C'Violent bully' fatally attacked
OL,4,Cpartner and waited 90 minutes to call
OL,5,C999
OL,7,F"Had he sought immediate medical
OL,8,Fattention after the fatal attack,
OL,9,Fthere is a chance Lisa could have
OL,10,Fsurvived. He chose instead to let her
OL,11,Fdie and then tried to cover up his
OL,12,Factions with lies.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
